| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0989 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 76ed65d3-a9db-5d7c-a7cf-bc7c1eecec26"
